        "order": 1,
        "text": "Mix brown sugar, paprika, salt, black pepper, garlic powder, onion powder, and cayenne pepper in a bowl to make the dry rub."
      },
      {
        "order": 2,
        "text": "Pat the pork shoulder dry and rub the spice mix all over it. Let it rest for at least 1 hour or overnight in the fridge for best flavor."
      },
      {
        "order": 3,
        "text": "Preheat oven to 130°C (265°F). Heat vegetable oil in a large ovenproof pot or Dutch oven over medium-high heat."
      },
      {
